    "body": "Package `bolt` is not building on `Ubuntu 18.04` for `ppc64le`. Likewise, not building for `CentOS 7` and `RHEL 7` for `ppc64le`. Using Spack @ develop (commit 958f26073efe340d5 from 18-March-2020). It is a `power8` host.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$> spack install bolt%gcc@7.3.0 target=ppc64le\r\n# fails with a verbose error, see full build log below\r\n# looks like scoping errors involving KMP_ macros, but I don't know\r\n```\r\n\r\nFull build log:  [bolt-ppc64le-build-log.txt](https://github.com/spack/spack/files/4350618/bolt-ppc64le-build-log.txt)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n@shintaro-iwasaki @raffenet \r\n\r\n",
